WarningsAsErrors: "*"

Checks:
  - clang-diagnostic-*,
  - bugprone-*,
  - cert-*,
  - concurrency-*,
  - misc-*,
  - mpi-*,
  - clang-analyzer-*,
  # Disabled because `fprintf_s` is not available on all platforms.
  - -clang-analyzer-security.insecureAPI.DeprecatedOrUnsafeBufferHandling
  # Disabled because fixed seed is intentional for consistent brick generation
  - -cert-msc51-cpp
